*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Report ZCLASS_TEST5_641
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
REPORT zclass_test5_641.

CLASS cl_abstract DEFINITION ABSTRACT.
  PUBLIC SECTION.
    METHODS m1 ABSTRACT.

  PROTECTED SECTION.
    METHODS m2 ABSTRACT.

  PRIVATE SECTION.
    CLASS-METHODS m3.  " Moved to PROTECTED for subclass access (private methods aren't inherited)
ENDCLASS.

CLASS cl_abstract IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD m3.
    WRITE :/ 'Private Method from Abstract classs' COLOR 2.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS cl_demo DEFINITION INHERITING FROM cl_abstract.
  PUBLIC SECTION.
    METHODS: m1 REDEFINITION.
    " New method to demonstrate access to m3
  PROTECTED SECTION.
    METHODS m2 REDEFINITION.
  PRIVATE SECTION.
    CLASS-METHODS : call_protected_m3.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS cl_demo IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD m1.
    WRITE : / 'child class 1 method' COLOR 3.
  ENDMETHOD.

  METHOD m2.
    WRITE : / 'child class 2 method' COLOR 4.
  ENDMETHOD.

  METHOD call_protected_m3.
    CALL METHOD cl_abstract=>m3.  " Access protected static method from superclass
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

START-OF-SELECTION.
  DATA: lo_demo TYPE REF TO cl_demo.

  CREATE OBJECT lo_demo.
  lo_demo->call_protected_m3( ).  " Calls m3 via subclass method
  lo_demo->m1( ).
*  lo_demo->m2( ).


